      "side": 1,
      "message": "This seems clunky. We\u0027re using two flags to track the same thing.\n\nj-\u003eremount_mode could default to MS_PRIVATE, and then minijail_set_remount_mode can do its thing, and minijail_skip_remount_private can just set it to zero. And if the flag is zero we don\u0027t call mount(2). Thoughts?",
